window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The gripping third installment of the Black Arrowhead series.</p> <p>Robyn is desperately searching for a pack, but the odds are stacked against her. Shifters don't accept humans, especially ones with a watchdog. Her fate takes a wild turn when she hitches a ride with a band of rogues who are vying for a spot in a newly formed pack. Just when she gets a taste of the good life, a menacing force threatens to rip it away.</p> <p>As a detective, Montana takes chances all the time. After seeing an open call for packmates, he gambles on an inexperienced Packmaster who has potential. When a mysterious woman joins their group, Montana defends her from those who would cast her out. Robyn is kind, loyal, and everything he desires. But when secrets are brought to light, they must each decide where their loyalty lies.</p> <p>A romance forms between an unlikely couple, but can love conquer all when the stakes are too high?</p> <p>Love takes courage.</p>"; 
